{"tid":842698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★窮人3大特質：一 懶、二 買股票、三 買iphoneXS","createTime":"2018-09-30T14:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:58:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6f87052a6ae719d62c9209eed5fdd2b9130453","tid":842698,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1883351/org/8c56cd42108d0f53bf37cbb791572bd9.jpg/AZzKu5twVE8dtlui_Nj6Ii_wOxs6reNxmjLYQZoy2EE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1883351%2Forg%2F8c56cd42108d0f53bf37cbb791572bd9.jpg%2FAZzKu5twVE8dtlui_Nj6Ii_wOxs6reNxmjLYQZoy2EE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5fe3e039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人窮的三大原因&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n1、懶惰&mdash;&mdash;甘願人生「戇居居」無所事事<br />\n<br />\n人懶就自不然賺錢更少，呢個道理係人都知。但市面上好多「專家」講話其實懶人先做到大老闆，勤力的人只會做到個好員工。其實呢個係一個偷換概念。成功創業的老闆，往往係懶做一些重複無聊的工序，而瘋狂地投入做真正有Value-adding的業務：無論係CEO親自Pitch一個大客，或斷定公司的戰略部署，或重大人事安排等等。<br />\n<br />\n2、貪心&mdash;&mdash;貪念蒙蔽了理性Judgment<br />\n<br />\n貪心同上進，有時真係一線之隔，而且成王敗寇。<span style=\"color: red;\">2005年，假如你孤注一擲買思捷環球，轉頭你辛辛苦苦儲落的錢就蒸發九成，一百萬變十萬</span>。但假如你孤注一擲買騰訊，咁你就會變做千萬甚至億萬富豪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3、揮霍： 大使成性，搵幾多都冇用<br />\n<br />\n呢個正正就係以上所講的收入相對支出比例，亦解釋到點解無論月入2萬同月入40萬的人，一樣可以好窮，或一樣可以好安逸。月入2萬的人，假如支出穩定地在1萬左右，咁其實個個月有錢剩，假以時日都會一筆儲蓄，可能都係唔夠買樓，但總算係有個錢傍身。有需要時都唔會「拿手唔成勢」。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，香港就有一位許姓前高官，身為香港第二把交椅，月入高達40萬，本應係社會上的超高收入人士，最終卻一樣落得破產地步，甚至因貪污相關罪行而鋃鐺入獄。本來，月入40萬，對大部份人來講等於「發達」。但對呢位官員，月入40萬，卻過住月入100萬先足夠的生活，揮霍無度，下下坐頭等飛London，出入超五星級酒店及天價餐廳。雖然風光一時，最終一樣變到「好窮」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/236476/%E4%BF%82%E7%AA%AE%E5%91%80-%E7%AA%AE%E4%BA%BA3%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%B9%E8%B3%AA-%E4%B8%80%E6%87%B6-%E4%BA%8C%E8%B2%AA-%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF-%E6%83%B3%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E7%A9%A9%E5%81%A5%E5%85%88%E8%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F236476%2F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E5%2591%2580-%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2587%25B6-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%25B2%25AA-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%258B%2599%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%2585%2588%25E8%25A6%2581&d=HsndlIiz%2Fi%2Fc61jSc1ST0kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=5b468d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/236476/%E4%BF%82%E7%AA%AE%E5%91%80-%E7%AA%AE%E4%BA%BA3%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%B9%E8%B3%AA-%E4%B8%80%E6%87%B6-%E4%BA%8C%E8%B2%AA-%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF-%E6%83%B3%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E7%A9%A9%E5%81%A5%E5%85%88%E8%A6%81</a>"},{"pid":"f911f77b18a2e15fcbd827b802972ff0951abe69","tid":842698,"uid":24660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"你中晒"},{"pid":"09702bc26cc94b01758ea302d523c23abe6fe3b4","tid":842698,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"4、做IT<br />\n人板&mdash;&mdash;腦魔"},{"pid":"79a5bd7fc729afd5d5f018c064d8459702a00443","tid":842698,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f911f77b18a2e15fcbd827b802972ff0951abe69","tid":842698,"uid":24660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"你中晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8518c9005645fa8713a4ff560772c3b46414ad","tid":842698,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09702bc26cc94b01758ea302d523c23abe6fe3b4","tid":842698,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"4、做IT<br />\n人板&mdash;&mdash;腦魔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e61f79328d9d393c23f60a63598a2c73fe208c","tid":842698,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":